 {"id":"franken_networkx-y5u6","title":"parity: graph family EdgeView objects should expose data() helper","description":"EdgeView objects across Graph, DiGraph, MultiGraph, and MultiDiGraph currently lack NetworkX's .data() helper. In FrankenNetworkX, list(G.edges.data()) and attribute forms like list(G.edges.data('weight', default='NA')) raise AttributeError, while upstream NetworkX exposes the helper and returns the expected edge-data iterables. Match the upstream EdgeView.data() helper contract across graph families.","status":"in_progress","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-21T08:57:14.121103048Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-21T08:57:38.557776795Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"franken_networkx-y6l","title":"Fix directed-graph semantics in recent Python algorithm bindings","description":"Recent fnx-python bindings for non_edges / all_pairs_dijkstra / average_node_connectivity / is_k_edge_connected incorrectly route DiGraph inputs through undirected semantics instead of matching NetworkX behavior.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-03-19T19:53:12.424624394Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-19T20:13:48.550002858Z","closed_at":"2026-03-19T20:13:48.549276753Z","close_reason":"Completed","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
-{"id":"franken_networkx-y7qf","title":"parity: graph classes should expose dict factory attributes and multigraph key factories","description":"Graph-family classes currently lack NetworkX's dict-factory attributes adjlist_inner_dict_factory, adjlist_outer_dict_factory, edge_attr_dict_factory, graph_attr_dict_factory, node_attr_dict_factory, and node_dict_factory. MultiGraph and MultiDiGraph also lack edge_key_dict_factory and new_edge_key(). Upstream exposes all of these; the dict factories materialize empty dicts by default, and new_edge_key('a','b') returns 1 on a graph that already has key 'k1'. Match the upstream factory/helper surface across the core graph classes.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-21T07:45:20.207108301Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-21T07:45:20.207108301Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
